Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:21.01,八犬-OP.JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow which GOD draw
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.01,0:02:21.98,八犬-OP.JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It believes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:24.35,八犬-OP.JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It does not believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:27.99,八犬-OP.JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can choose MY  FATE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:35.11,八犬-OP.JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾いた風に　抱かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:41.64,八犬-OP.JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命への神秘を覚え　刻む想い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:45.06,八犬-OP.JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ただ　傍にいたいと願い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:47.64,八犬-OP.JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人を愛し　人を憎み
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:51.41,八犬-OP.JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲しさは優しさ生む
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:56.36,八犬-OP.JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,たとえ光が　消えたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:03:01.19,八犬-OP.JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日の希望を探すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.19,0:03:05.14,八犬-OP.JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃えた血の呼吸　引き寄せれば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:10.28,八犬-OP.JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因果は奇跡に変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:12.54,八犬-OP.JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop! Don't wanna rests!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.44,八犬-OP.JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow which GOD draw
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:18.50,八犬-OP.JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇を掻き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:22.43,八犬-OP.JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手を伸ばすよ　どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:24.95,八犬-OP.JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This heart was asking
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:28.37,八犬-OP.JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつか還るまで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:33.02,八犬-OP.JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙の意味　無駄にはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:37.92,八犬-OP.JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋のように　蠢く果てに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:41.47,八犬-OP.JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吠えて交わる　FATE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:42.68,八犬-OP.JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,hell!
